When a BB/Epic Guild is called in, it should be *only* members of that guild, <br>
<br>
For instance: if Guild A is a BB guild, and they are called in, but do not have enough members on-line, they should not be able to have Guild B, who is NOT a BB/Epic Guild *help* them.<br>
